# Windsurf AI Rules — @stsgs/ui Project

# Auto-generated from ai-rules/core.md by `npx stsgs ai sync`

## Architecture
6-layer dependency: tokens/ → ui/ → sections/ → features/ → hooks/ → providers/
NEVER import from upper to lower layer.

## Anti-Monolith Rules
1. Component ≤ 150 lines, File ≤ 200 lines, Page ≤ 40 lines
2. Max 3 useState → extract to hook
3. No data fetching in components
4. Barrel exports always
5. Layer separation enforced
6. Dynamic imports for heavy deps
7. ESLint active

## Component Discovery
Check first: `npx stsgs list [layer]`
Add: `npx stsgs add <component>`
NEVER recreate existing components.

## Stack: Next.js 16, React 19, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Radix UI
